Suarez was banned for seven games for biting Ottman Bakkal while playing for Ajax in 2010, and received a further 10-game ban for biting Chelsea defender Branislav Ivanovic in April 2013.

Uruguay are due to fly back to their Sao Paolo base on Wednesday before traveling to Rio to face Colombia in the last 16 next Monday.

